# AI Instructions for this project

## File Edits
- Never rewrite an entire file when editing it, only change relevant parts, unless necessary.
- never create README files, unless explicitly asked to.
- Don't try to build or run the project, unless specified to.
- Don't be verbose when explaining changes made, and avoid explaining unless necessary.
- Never generate assets like SVGs unless specified to.
- Prefer to use shadcn components.
- Prefer using absolute path with aliases unless file is in the same directory.
- when editing, don't try to fix formatting manually. 

## Components
- Use the DataTable component for all tables - any extra features added to DataTable must not break existing implementations unless specifically requested.
- Use the modal component for all modals.

## Styling
- prefer using Tailwind data- attributes over conditional classes.
